the question is:
examination management system:
file handling method used to store records of students ina particular database file where you can perform operations
such as add/del the details of the student, monitoring the attendace, set eligibility criteria for exams, check eligible students,
room allotment for eligible students based on branch / semester. display all records of the student.

functions
1. add/del
2. attendance
3. eligibility criteria
4. check eligibility
5. room allotment for eligible students based on branch / semester

database structure:
per student we will have:
1 admission number
2 name
3 attendance (present or absent)
4 science marks
5 math marks
6 english marks
7 branch
8 semester

